{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":2,"day":29}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"颗颗红心向太阳部队学习毛主席著作歌谣选","authors":["李宗照王怀明雷锋段成法李连瑞王怀明杨涵戈一兵标圆员高澄泉廖初江王梦今高顺华李佑田高博学杨季春杨继光冉庆华王宇洪炉远明王全博"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花没有太阳不能开放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花没有太阳不能开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼没有雨露不能生长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个人没有毛泽东思想来武装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要迷失政治方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（“南京路上好八连”战士 李宗照）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的感想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊象父亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席思想象太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲时刻关怀我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳培育我成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（雷锋）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“神灯”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是“神灯”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引导战士向前奔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立场坚定如磐石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志昂扬头脑清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（助教 汪德元）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想照我心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想照我心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚稳眼亮头脑清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五好鲜花开不败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓做红色接班人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（济南部队）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛选”，“毛选”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛选”“毛选”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一字一句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注入我心坎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（班长 段成法）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读《为人民服务》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿学雷锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼得一身红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨尽个人锈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永做螺丝钉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死为人民死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生为人民生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（战士 李连瑞）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进步两条根 ——读毛主席著作笔记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进步两条根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内因和外因；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外因是条件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内因是根本；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两者结合紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能得上进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（装甲部队）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”就象红太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”就象红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句字字闪金光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光普照全世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱除黑暗迎曙光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精读“毛著”胸怀阔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命斗志倍增长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（海军战士）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作放光芒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句字字指方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作好比顺风船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破浪无阻挡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛雪亮看千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"糊涂思想一扫光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（炮手 王怀明）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连队气象万千"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连队气象万千，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官兵干劲冲天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根本原因一条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席思想领先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（战士 戈一兵）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“及时雨”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨出座舱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳出飞机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，小伙子多么神气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个夸奖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个赞誉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子高兴得面带笑意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是啊！头次单飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是五分成绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这激动的心情怎能压抑？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可他话到嘴边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽又向墙边走去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙上，有两行闪光的诗句”——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“虚心使人进步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骄傲使人落后。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两句话犹如一场及时雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子看在眼里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记在心里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的教诲将终生记忆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（飞行学员 张连三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士读了觉悟高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争永不忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立场站得牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士读了耐苦劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传统大发扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱枪又爱镐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字句句都是宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为革命守海防，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根儿扎得牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（海岛战士）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当我打开“毛选”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当我打开“毛选”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽出一张书签，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见一个微笑的面孔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话儿就响在耳边："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席著作是粮食，是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武器，是方向盘……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我捧书细细阅读，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句扣住心弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象在革命的大路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到了明灯盏盏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当我读完一篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再看看那张笑脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说一声：“安息吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席的话我已牢记心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要象你那样活学活用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象你那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把有限的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投入无限的为人民服务里边。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（标图员 高澄泉）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读《愚公移山》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一学《愚公移山》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长了志气不怕难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愚公能把山搬走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锹一镐不空谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二学《愚公移山》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依靠集体不孤单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民头上三座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全民奋战齐推翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三学《愚公移山》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢于斗争破难关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战略藐视敢胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战术重视不蛮干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四学《愚公移山》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树立正确世界观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人的因素是第一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士面前没困难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（装甲兵某部廖初江）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无价宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是无价宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛过仙丹灵芝草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学过“毛著”脑开窍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲倍增立场牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（沈阳部队）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百战百胜无阻挡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作象太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得心里亮堂堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩风劈浪冲向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百战百胜无阻挡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（中印边界边防部队烈士王梦令）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是灯塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得战士心开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕困难它再大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱用毅力征服它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军训打靶是优秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间操作无偏差；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治思想觉悟高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准戴五好光荣花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是灯塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得战士心开花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗时候想起它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇机智把敌杀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行军时候想起它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神振奋不疲乏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远学习它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大立功劳来报答。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（学员 杨季春）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习《纪念白求恩》前后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习前："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望山区唉声叹气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当炊事员真没出息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"论前途真成问题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个人主义到处扯皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习后："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望山区欢天喜地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当炊事员真了不起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"论前途光明远大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命工作一生到底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（战士 李佑田）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小红书囊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小红书囊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”里边装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上课和开会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时带身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争得一分读一分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年受益闯四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（战士 高顺华）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是法宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是法宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切工作离不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战士有了它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举目能穿九重霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是法宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句真理要记牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头脑有它来武装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立场坚定不动摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是法宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命靠它来指导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方巨人奔天堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠它给咱搭金桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（武汉部队 高博学）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越学心越亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮位里，坐一圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都来学“毛选”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读一句，想三想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越学心里越亮堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学了“毛选”练武艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身上下是力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼更明，手更稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞄得准，打得狠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靶子开了花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌机难逃遁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问力量哪里来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导记在心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（海军 冉庆华）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作到军营"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作到军营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军营一片欢呼声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天有了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"训练开门红；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天有了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈日下面练雄兵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天有了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪枪打在靶中心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天有了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰冻三尺不嫌冷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年四季不离你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人当上五好兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（北京部队 杨继光）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日一轮抱怀中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日一轮抱怀中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空军战士驾战鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想武装我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空万里筑长城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（飞行员 王全博）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天学“毛著”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天学“毛著”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天有进步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天不学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中不舒服。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（济南部队）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（本版插图：王宇、洪炉、远明）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}